1
00:00:03,820 --> 00:00:05,500
I'm doomed.

2
00:00:39,229 --> 00:00:41,781
Madam Zhu, I didn't mean to offend you.

3
00:00:42,030 --> 00:00:43,470
Don't scare me.

4
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:50,741
Who's there?

5
00:00:51,152 --> 00:00:52,920
Who's pulling a prank there?

6
00:00:53,032 --> 00:00:55,210
Listen. I'm not afraid.

7
00:01:08,616 --> 00:01:13,260
=Mysterious Tales of Chang'an=

8
00:01:13,266 --> 00:01:15,160
=Episode 5=

9
00:01:50,816 --> 00:01:51,557
Do you feel better?

10
00:01:53,690 --> 00:01:55,020
Am I poisoned?

11
00:01:56,690 --> 00:01:57,989
I went to the Court of Judicial Review

12
00:01:58,189 --> 00:02:00,000
during the hours of you disappearance.

13
00:02:00,010 --> 00:02:01,000
The herbalist said

14
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:02,717
the centipede is not
a Central Plains species,

15
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,381
but a South Sea species.

16
00:02:04,768 --> 00:02:05,980
It spreads poison.

17
00:02:06,460 --> 00:02:07,170
This poison

18
00:02:07,421 --> 00:02:09,768
is highly hallucinogenic
and disorienting.

19
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,848
The Central Plains call it Gu Poison.

20
00:02:15,133 --> 00:02:16,314
What about this medicine?

21
00:02:17,205 --> 00:02:18,256
It seems that this medicine

22
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:20,610
can cure the poison.

23
00:02:22,093 --> 00:02:23,578
You saved my life.

24
00:02:24,536 --> 00:02:26,085
I'll take you as my master.

25
00:02:26,770 --> 00:02:27,410
Master.

26
00:02:27,456 --> 00:02:28,020
Let me finish.

27
00:02:29,060 --> 00:02:31,568
I've seen these two
costumed wackos before.

28
00:02:31,690 --> 00:02:34,258
It was so creepy
I didn't dare do anything.

29
00:02:34,730 --> 00:02:36,845
I can't let them
get away now. Wait for me.

30
00:03:22,580 --> 00:03:24,100
Stop playing tricks.

31
00:03:24,189 --> 00:03:26,533
You're tall.
You're on stilts, aren't you?

32
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:31,410
I noticed it as early as
the first time I met you.

33
00:03:31,690 --> 00:03:35,249
The ground you walked on has
no footprints, only round hollows.

34
00:03:35,402 --> 00:03:37,394
It was caused by stilt sticks, right?

35
00:05:56,020 --> 00:05:57,402
You are just a puppet of the murderer.

36
00:05:58,256 --> 00:06:00,568
You will suffer for a while.

37
00:06:00,792 --> 00:06:03,234
When the poison is relieved and you've
recovered your senses, go home.

38
00:06:35,980 --> 00:06:37,760
Master, how is it going?

39
00:06:39,205 --> 00:06:39,808
Meng.

40
00:06:44,650 --> 00:06:45,858
He had been poisoned.

41
00:06:46,210 --> 00:06:48,434
I stopped him from
pulling any more tricks.

42
00:06:55,034 --> 00:06:56,394
This well...

43
00:06:58,592 --> 00:07:00,141
It does seem a bit odd.

44
00:07:02,208 --> 00:07:03,776
It is said that Madam Zhu died

45
00:07:04,213 --> 00:07:06,090
in the backyard well a month ago.

46
00:07:06,730 --> 00:07:08,117
So this must be it.

47
00:07:16,045 --> 00:07:16,960
Master.

48
00:07:17,330 --> 00:07:18,690
I'm kind of scared.

49
00:07:18,976 --> 00:07:19,786
Don't call me master.

50
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,082
I didn't promise to take
you on as a disciple.

51
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:28,220
I saw two people

52
00:07:28,338 --> 00:07:31,189
in weird costumes before.

53
00:07:31,282 --> 00:07:32,410
And now

54
00:07:33,820 --> 00:07:34,850
there's only one.

55
00:07:35,082 --> 00:07:37,000
There is only one?

56
00:07:37,045 --> 00:07:38,980
Then the other one...

57
00:07:40,690 --> 00:07:42,200
should be heading to Zuihua House.

58
00:07:42,493 --> 00:07:44,202
The murderer will continue to kill.

59
00:07:44,304 --> 00:07:46,610
Master, hurry up and
protect Lan and the others.

60
00:07:50,869 --> 00:07:51,770
Then take care of yourself.


